</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-05-02-0016-0002-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-05-02-0016-0002-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>GW signed his endorsement: Receivd at Fort Loudoun this 6th day of Novr 1757.</p>

